.TH "nvme_init_get_log_support_cap_config_list" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_support_cap_config_list" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_support_cap_config_list \- Initialize passthru command for Supported Capacity Configuration List
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_support_cap_config_list
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u16 domid "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_supported_cap_config_list_log *cap "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "domid" 12
Domain Identifier selection, if supported
.IP "cap" 12
User address to store supported capabilities config list
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_SUPPORTED_CAP_CONFIG_LIST
